data.description: Perfect entertaining retreat in Richland Chambers Reservoir community! This 2 story home features a master suite with jacuzzi and 4 additional suite-mate style bedrooms upstairs. Walk-in closets throughout, game room/loft area, open kitchen/living/dining concept, large utility room, separate office. Storage galore! Incredible covered back porch compliments the backyard oasis with a water view. Workshop has electric and RV plug-in and drive-in ramp. HOA boat ramp access.
